{"tid":880030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣好抽離","createTime":"2018-10-28T12:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T13:11:58.000Z","uid":23277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed71c7ac8b9217b81ed2fbeccbe0e5b5efc90153","tid":880030,"uid":23277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"其實我平時唔會放負<br />\n我知冇人鐘意同負能量既人做朋友<br />\n<br />\n自己幾年前經歷啲事<br />\n可以話長大左<br />\n發現到care愈少個人會愈開心<br />\n慢慢連自己既事都唔care唔敢咁上心<br />\n我怕有期望再會失望<br />\n<br />\n呢期好煩<br />\n我連自己既事都冇care<br />\n搞到宜家好多事迫在眉睫<br />\n好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n另一邊<br />\n呢幾年都有女仔埋我身<br />\n但全部都冇feel所以我冇沉船好抽離<br />\n<br />\n最近有個女仔<br />\n大家都有feel <br />\n佢有主動過<br />\n但我仍然好抽離唔知自己想點投入唔到<br />\n因為我怕再經歷<br />\n&quot;然而全冇用投入所有已斷送&quot;既感覺<br />\n<br />\n再另一邊<br />\n自己係個識social既毒撚<br />\n享受私人空間<br />\n但每次自摺就會覺得好冇productivity好鬱悶<br />\n我都知多啲見人心情會好啲<br />\n但我又懶唔想出街<br />\n&quot;活像個孤獨患者自我拉扯&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底我可以點做<br />\n好討厭宜家既自己"},{"pid":"1fdaac9eaed286f906c943eb00edd16d8a6c5241","tid":880030,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"啲嘢似到咁， 差啲以為自己開咗post"},{"pid":"6c467044cddda995ce71f95bd41da35bb18e2611","tid":880030,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"仲以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be313c8bdf21abf2e62bae853987e1ced6eef617","tid":880030,"uid":23277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T12:51:57.000Z","msg":"樓上2位我地攬下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd6157d92b0ead7799dab9619ab1fc51aaac636","tid":880030,"uid":132834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T12:56:43.000Z","msg":"做咩扮我開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40494ef274f88be8b53cf64aded5147321cc60e1","tid":880030,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201